{
  "info": {
    "name": "Convocatorias USCO - API",
    "description": "Coleccion para el Sistema de Gestion de Convocatorias Institucionales (Universidad Surcolombiana).\n\nUso:\n1. Ejecuta `Auth > Login` con las credenciales del administrador semilla. El access token y el refresh token se guardan automaticamente en las variables de coleccion `token` y `refreshToken`.\n2. El resto de peticiones heredan la autenticacion Bearer (access token).\n3. Cuando el access token expire (15 min), ejecuta `Auth > Refresh` para renovarlo sin volver a iniciar sesion.\n\nNota: los identificadores de la API estan en ingles (name, email, callId...). Los mensajes de error vienen en espanol.\n\nVariables:\n- baseUrl: URL del backend (por defecto http://localhost:8080)\n- token / refreshToken: se completan solos tras el login\n- userId / callId / categoryId / applicationId: ids de ejemplo, ajusta segun tus datos.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "callId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "categoryId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "applicationId", "value": "1" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "  pm.test('Access token recibido', () => pm.expect(body.accessToken).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "} else {",
                  "  pm.test('Login fallido', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@usco.edu.co\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin123*\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "refresh"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Usuarios",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar usuarios",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/usuarios", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "usuarios"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener usuario",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/usuarios/{{userId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "usuarios", "{{userId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear usuario (estudiante)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"identification\": \"1075123456\",\n  \"name\": \"Laura Estudiante\",\n  \"email\": \"laura@usco.edu.co\",\n  \"password\": \"Estudiante123*\",\n  \"role\": \"ESTUDIANTE\",\n  \"status\": \"ACTIVO\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/usuarios", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "usuarios"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear usuario (docente)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"identification\": \"7712345\",\n  \"name\": \"Carlos Docente\",\n  \"email\": \"carlos@usco.edu.co\",\n  \"password\": \"Docente123*\",\n  \"role\": \"DOCENTE\",\n  \"status\": \"ACTIVO\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/usuarios", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "usuarios"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar usuario",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Laura Estudiante Actualizada\",\n  \"email\": \"laura@usco.edu.co\",\n  \"role\": \"ESTUDIANTE\",\n  \"status\": \"ACTIVO\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/usuarios/{{userId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "usuarios", "{{userId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Eliminar usuario",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/usuarios/{{userId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "usuarios", "{{userId}}"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
